    "The results show that CIA with uniform sampling outperforms the dense sampling-based methods.",
    "This observation confirms the findings in Chen et al. (2021), which emphasizes that uniform sampling usually allows the network to learn more information.",
    "We also observe that our UDA approach achieves state-of-the-art results for both dense and uniform samplings.",
